ty to work in a fast paced environment Detail oriented Excellent organizational skills Ability to create an environment where employees can thrive Strong written and verbal communication skills Bar Manager related job titles: Pub Manager Tavern Manager Restaurant Manager Assistant Bar Manager (Part-Time) Front Of House Manager Ready to find your next hire? Post a Job Â© 2020 SH Inc. |Â PrivacyÂ |Â TermsÂ |Â Privacy CenterÂ  |Â Do Not Sell My Personal Information"
